  - family-names: "Isaksson"
    given-names: "Ola"
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0373-3720"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/alex-pradas/DUCTILE"
keywords:
  - large language models
  - agent-based design
  - design automation
  - design methodology
  - design process
  - product development
  - expert systems
  - design evaluation
abstract: "Engineering analysis automation in product development relies on rigid interfaces between tools, data formats and documented processes. This paper presents DUCTILE (Delegated, User-supervised Coordination of Tool- and document-Integrated LLM-Enabled), an approach for developing, executing and evaluating LLM-based agentic automation of engineering analysis tasks."
